{"tid":1040660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果踢爆：聯乘鞋貨不對辦 CDG心心甩眼","createTime":"2019-02-28T08:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T10:16:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5807df5695a293101dd7ee36fe049e24538ad7","tid":1040660,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190228/20622624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190228%2F20622624&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=7d66471d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190228%2F20622624&h=430ecb9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190228/20622624</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果踢爆：聯乘鞋貨不對辦 CDG心心甩眼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190228/large/28ls4p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F28ls4p5.jpg&h=aa4bde30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃小姐在網店買的兩對聯乘鞋疑是假貨。<br />\n<br />\n市民黃小姐同樣在IG遇上騙徒，她在一家網店購入兩對時尚設計師川久保玲及品牌Converse合作推出的便服鞋，但發現貨不對辦，多處與真貨不同，尤其鞋面心形圖案的眼晴「鬥雞」，疑購得假貨，共損失近1,700元。<br />\n<br />\n黃小姐去年12月瀏覽IG，發現一家網店登廣告稱聖誕促銷，標榜「持有效商業登記」、經營「日本美國波鞋服飾代購」、「正貨正品信心保證」，並於葵涌大連排道貴盛工業大廈設貨倉。黃小姐見該網站有售川久保玲設計的COMME des GARCONS Play X Converse鞋款，價格僅800多元，較坊間每對售價最少1,100元便宜，即向對方查詢是否真貨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：蘋果踢爆：騙徒IG賣炒款假波鞋21歲仔失財13萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同一對鞋一越南製一印尼製<br />\n<br />\n賣家回覆聲稱是真貨，之後更應黃小姐要求傳來從外國入貨單據，顯示銀碼總值1.8萬元英鎊，並解釋是大量入貨貨單。黃小姐不虞有詐，以近1,700元購入兩款便服鞋。但黃小姐收到賣家寄來的兩對鞋後，發現貨不對辦，懷疑買到假貨。<br />\n<br />\n「鞋盒同真貨嘅樣、大細都唔同，最慘係其中一對鞋嘅標籤，一隻寫越南製，另一隻就寫印尼製。左腳鞋面心形圖案嘅眼睛仲要係『鬥雞』，鞋墊上同一個心形圖案嘅一對眼，着咗一日就甩色冇咗對眼！」事後黃小姐向賣方要求退款，但對方已失蹤。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n蘋果踢爆：騙徒IG賣炒款假波鞋 21歲仔失財13萬<br />\n<br />\n蘋果踢爆：騙徒IG賣炒款假波鞋21歲仔失財13萬"},{"pid":"f9b52e649b83d7bde2f59befc38186e7f82b0b74","tid":1040660,"uid":51183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"要幾白痴先會響ig/fb買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52361721092f108af69dbbc8210b47038f3a1ec","tid":1040660,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"一次係咁<br />\n兩次係咁<br />\n到底中計個D人坐左幾耐"},{"pid":"33f315a5a013d22b921015efdfdd201e26580de0","tid":1040660,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵俾人呃啦，"},{"pid":"a966b8658afee7467fac5240ac82fe6782a3ab9e","tid":1040660,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"係咁煲緊d ig騙案<br />\n跟住就推d網絡監管條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad4f573bdc1924c2c317fa612e1e1e498b9d36d","tid":1040660,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"2019仲有on9仔係ig買野"},{"pid":"a2e04dee5d7c0d8270f0c9bf8462eedb30596c43","tid":1040660,"uid":98795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45d121f0cb92957ae25aa0f9b85e1842ffbd926","tid":1040660,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"This is 黃小姐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}